{"tid":2080401,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"嚴防被印度人裝修  小米門市招牌換「印度製造」","createTime":"2020-06-26T11:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-26T13:01:56.000Z","uid":5195,"like":3,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"09763dc7e70c6f35d3c86c98c8d68c6cf1bc3e98","tid":2080401,"uid":5195,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:42:39.000Z","msg":"印度《商業旗幟報》（Business Standard）6月24日引述華企高層人員的消息報道，來自中國的品牌如小米、Vivo、OnePlus與RealMe等，都在落力向零售夥伴、工廠工人等傳遞「我們公司很本土」的訊息，例如逾9成員工是印度人、全部零售商來自印度等，又會強調公司在印度有大的投資，設立生產基地及研發基地等。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體又發現，小米在印度加爾各答（Kolkata）的門市掛上「Made in India」（印度製造）的標語來遮蓋招牌，小米又指示門市員工不用穿制服，避免有遭人襲擊的風險。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://akm-img-a-in.tosshub.com/indiatoday/images/story/202006/IMG_20200625_121904-770x433.jpeg?7.zJSjFb4EHXXnoHIDMOJI3ImH8c4hu7\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fakm-img-a-in.tosshub.com%2Findiatoday%2Fimages%2Fstory%2F202006%2FIMG_20200625_121904-770x433.jpeg%3F7.zJSjFb4EHXXnoHIDMOJI3ImH8c4hu7&h=5ef794e9&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"81590e68477bbcc465ca2c8d459cdc6fcd827b26","tid":2080401,"uid":194326,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:43:46.000Z","msg":"倒米<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06b66e80ed94a39f7ae63bb9bb497e4538cafe0f","tid":2080401,"uid":109923,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:45:02.000Z","msg":"個牌子叫made in india？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a5f6b9544d6d5b1904cda975a4622e249a2a00cc","tid":2080401,"uid":83348,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:48:13.000Z","msg":"喂，印度佬，班終國人當你哋傻架，世界上有google map 架嘛<br />\n<br />\n你哋唔係咁都唔放火燒佢哋呀？"},{"pid":"224c527bef0c8715d642bbfe14958e5c7f0d4fd6","tid":2080401,"uid":252142,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-26T11:49:36.000Z","msg":"算唔算此地無銀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"088e27bbebe0ae328de862